title: Stay Stay Stay (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor penned this upbeat song with no one particular in mind at the time.. Maybe after all the turmoil, she was feeling a little hopeful! So what is this song about? We break it all down!
And up next, we are fulfilling a listener's request! What would you like to hear from us? Let us know and we just might be able to do it for you! There are lots of ways to reach us!
